Begging for water.

1785
01:59:02.000 --> 01:59:10.000
So these guys find a route. I don't want to make it sound like they found some easy escape route that's going to work.

1786
01:59:10.000 --> 01:59:16.000
They found a possible way of getting out of this perimeter. And when they get back,

1787
